lead_paragraph: On the mound in the seventh inning for the first time this season, Matt Harvey gave up his first walk of the game and his second hit, leading to a sacrifice bunt and a second-and-third jam.

headline.print_headline: Harvey Rediscovers Form, Leads Mets Over White Sox 1-0
